5^n - 5^{n-3} = 5^{n-3} *124
a^b\cdot a^c = a^{b+c}
5^n = 5^{(n - 3)+ 3} = 5^{n -3}\cdot 5^3
5^{n-3}
\begin{align}5^n - 5^{n-3} & = \underbrace{\color{blue}{5^{n-3}}\cdot 5^3}_{\large =\,5^n} - \color{blue}{5^{n-3}}\cdot 1 \\ \\ & = \color{blue}{5^{n-3}}(5^3 - 1) \\ \\& = 5^{n - 3}\cdot 124\end{align}
